<translation id="1284343625991453987">Njia ya Mkato ya Ecosia</translation>
<translation id="5953954252731207958">Hujatembelea hivi majuzi. Chrome imeondoa <ph name="PERMISSION"/></translation>
<translation id="6003112304606738118">Inapakua... Zimesalia saa <ph name="HOURS"/></translation>
<translation id="6014316319780893079">Kwa kutumia <ph name="BEGIN_LINK"/>zana kutoka Chrome<ph name="END_LINK"/>, unaweza kuvinjari kwa usalama na kuwa na udhibiti</translation>
<translation id="4767994371234572952">Weka mapendeleo kwenye Ecosia iwe unavyopenda</translation>
<translation id="5490755016715767023">Ecosia itazima kisha iwake baada ya <ph name="REMAINING_TIME"/></translation>
<translation id="6040143037577758943">Funga</translation>
<translation id="6070348360322141662">Kwa usalama wa ziada, Google Chrome itasimba data yako kwa njia fiche</translation>
