<translation id="6134085236017727171">Ili utumie maikrofoni yako, ruhusu Chrome ifikie <ph name="BEGIN_LINK"/>mipangilio ya mfumo<ph name="END_LINK"/></translation>
<translation id="4618410489751241263">Vichupo hivi vinatumia nyenzo za ziada. Ruhusu Ecosia ivifanye visitumike ili kuboresha utendaji wako.</translation>
